Pizza Masters - Season 1, Episode 3




City of Cousinly Love - Philadelphia, PA

Fran and Sal are in Philadelphia to look for spots to open a new Artichoke Pizza. To ensure their success, they hit up successful multi-generational family restaurants who know how to succeed for the long haul in the City of Brotherly Love.
